A well-balanced formula with Salmon as the primary ingredient and main protein source for proper muscle development. Salmon meal is also an abundant source of Omega-3 Essential Fatty Acids, DHA and EPA, to promote proper brain development and function. This puppy formula also contains the Prebiotic Galacto-Oligosaccharide, naturally found in mother’s milk; Inulin to boost immunity; and a special mix of vitamins and minerals for total nutrition of puppies.

product.Product Tittle for ecom: SmartHeart Veggie Pack Veg Dog Food-3 kg
product.Product Description:
Adverse food reaction could be found in some dogs or some specific breeds. Causes of this reaction could be rooted to animal proteins that are used in dog food in general, for example, chicken or beef, which are not easy to digest. Also, dongs consuming the same type of protein for a long period could be inflicted to this problem.

The symptoms that could easily be seen included dried skin, skin dermatitis, itchiness, rash, skin flakes. These affect not only dogs physical and mental wellbeing, but also the owners.

SmartHeart Veggie Pack is suitable for sensitive dogs, formulating using only best ingredient from quality soy protein. SmartHeart Veggie Pack is easily digestible, eliminating factors to cause skin irritation, and providing all essential nutrition for your dog to stay healthy and strong.

product.Product Tittle for ecom: SmartHeart Chicken and Liver Flavor Dry Dog Food Small breed (Adult)
product.Product Description: Small breed dogs require a different kind of diet. A specially formulated food to match their size and activity level is essential in order for them to receive a complete and balanced nutrition. SmartHeart® small breed dog food is formulated to meet small breed dogs’ nutritional requirements using the best quality ingredients and supplemented with fish oil (rich in DHA and Omega3 fatty acid) and Lecithin (rich in Choline) to help enhance brain and nervous system function and promote heart health. Its special crunchy kibble texture is designed to help reduce dental plaque.
